"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-simone-biles-was-wearing-a-goat-necklace\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Simone Biles won the gold medal in the women's all-around gymnastics competition at the Paris Olympics to cement her legacy as the GOAT.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 136, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a term that gets thrown around pretty loosely these days, but if anyone has actually earned the title, it's Biles, themost decorated gymnast in Team USA history.\", \"from\": 137, \"to\": 303, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 286, \"end\": 294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.5339145211232793, \"rank\": 0.7743742997197448, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After winning her second all-around individual goldshe put on a goat necklace.\", \"from\": 305, \"to\": 383, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"the GOAT@Simone_Bileswearing a goat necklace \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0090\\u0090pic.twitter.com/PP2DofrI2B  This was the first time that Biles had worn a goat.\", \"from\": 385, \"to\": 513, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She went through a period where she wore leotards with the formidable animal stitched into the design.\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 616, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Simone Biles (@simonebiles)  Here's what Biles toldMarie Claireabout the designs in 2021:  The idea was to hit back at the haters.\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 765, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 635, \"end\": 647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not feel like it was necessarily fair how they could keep saying whatever they wanted, but then if I said something, it wasn't fair.\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 904, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"[The haters] were joking like, \\\"I swear, if she put a goat on her leo, blah, blah, blah.\\\"\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That would make them so angry.\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1025, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And then I was like, \\\"Oh, that's actually a good idea.\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1080, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us make the haters hate it, and the fans love it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1135, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The haters have been silenced for now, which means her necklace is more a declaration of fact than a response.\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1247, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stephen Douglas is a Senior Writer on the Breaking & Trending News Team at Sports Illustrated.\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1249, \"end\": 1264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_A._Douglas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.825619720573781e-20, \"text\": \"Stephen Douglas\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_A._Douglas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_A._Douglas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has been in journalism and media since 2008, and now casts a wide net with coverage across all sports.\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1449, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stephen spent more than a decade with The Big Lead and has previously written for Uproxx and The Sporting News.\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1532, \"end\": 1538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uproxx\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4465747782803924e-22, \"text\": \"Uproxx\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uproxx\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uproxx\"}, {\"begin\": 1547, \"end\": 1560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sporting_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.046016442394699e-14, \"text\": \"Sporting News\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sporting_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sporting_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has three children, two degrees and one now unverified Twitter account.\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1636, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1620, \"end\": 1627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.450466129780077e-16, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Stephen_Douglas  \\u00c2\\u00a9 2025ABG-SI LLC- SPORTS ILLUSTRATED IS A REGISTERED TRADEMARK OF ABG-SI LLC.\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1740, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"- All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1763, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The content on this site is for entertainment and educational purposes only.\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1840, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Betting and gambling content is intended for individuals 21+ and is based on individual commentators' opinions and not that of Sports Illustrated or its affiliates, licensees and related brands.\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 2035, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1968, \"end\": 1986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.4600164297189605e-13, \"text\": \"Sports Illustrated\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All picks and predictions are suggestions only and not a guarantee of success or profit.\", \"from\": 2036